    </div>

    <!-- Translation notes -->
    <h3>Translation notes</h3>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Convolution in signal processing flips the kernel; in deep learning, cross-correlation (no flip) is standard but still called "convolution." The Scheme code above implements cross-correlation. In practice, learned kernels absorb the flip.</p>

